@startuml
!theme plain
title "Диаграмма последовательности – обработка документа (загрузка → распознавание → сохранение)"

actor "Пользователь" as Client
participant "DocumentController\n(Spring)" as Controller
participant "DocumentProcessingService" as ProcessingService
participant "FileStorageService" as FileStorage
participant "MLServiceClient" as MLClient
participant "MLService\n(FastAPI)" as MLService
participant "DocumentRepository" as DocRepo
participant "CounterpartyRepository" as CpRepo
database "База данных" as DB

Client -> Controller: POST /documents/upload\n(file, metadata)
activate Controller

Controller -> ProcessingService: processDocument(file, fileId)
activate ProcessingService

ProcessingService -> FileStorage: saveFile(file, fileId)
activate FileStorage
FileStorage --> ProcessingService: storagePath
deactivate FileStorage

ProcessingService -> DocRepo: save(new Document(status=UPLOADED))
activate DocRepo
DocRepo --> DB: insert
DB --> DocRepo: ok
DocRepo --> ProcessingService: Document entity
deactivate DocRepo

ProcessingService -> MLClient: classifyDocument(fileBytes, fileId, debug=false)
activate MLClient

MLClient -> MLService: POST /classify\n(multipart/form-data)
activate MLService

note right of MLService
  Внутри MLService:
  1. Предобработка изображения
     (ImagePreprocessor)
  2. OCR через Tesseract
     (OCREngine)
  3. Классификация типа документа
     (DocumentClassifier)
  4. Извлечение реквизитов
     (FieldExtractor)
end note

MLService --> MLClient: ClassificationResponse\n(documentType, confidence,\n documentNumber, documentDate,\n totalAmount, counterpartyName,\n counterpartyInn, counterpartyKpp,\n rawText, ...)
deactivate MLService

MLClient --> ProcessingService: ClassificationResponse
deactivate MLClient

ProcessingService -> ProcessingService: validateExtractedFields(response)
note right: Проверка ИНН (10/12 цифр),\nКПП (9 цифр),\nналичие обязательных полей

alt Валидация успешна
    ProcessingService -> CpRepo: findByInn(counterpartyInn)
    activate CpRepo
    CpRepo --> DB: select
    DB --> CpRepo: Counterparty (или null)
    CpRepo --> ProcessingService: existing or null
    deactivate CpRepo

    alt Контрагент не найден
        ProcessingService -> CpRepo: save(new Counterparty(...))
        activate CpRepo
        CpRepo --> DB: insert
        DB --> CpRepo: Counterparty with id
        CpRepo --> ProcessingService: savedCounterparty
        deactivate CpRepo
    end

    ProcessingService -> DocRepo: update Document\n(set documentType, documentNumber,\n documentDate, totalAmount,\n counterparty, status=PROCESSED,\n extractedText, rawMlResponse)
    activate DocRepo
    DocRepo --> DB: update
    DB --> DocRepo: ok
    DocRepo --> ProcessingService: updated Document
    deactivate DocRepo

    ProcessingService --> Controller: DocumentResponse (success)
    Controller --> Client: 200 OK + данные документа

else Валидация не пройдена
    ProcessingService -> DocRepo: update Document\n(set status=VALIDATION_FAILED,\n errorMessage, processedAt)
    activate DocRepo
    DocRepo --> DB: update
    DB --> DocRepo: ok
    deactivate DocRepo

    ProcessingService --> Controller: DocumentResponse (with warnings)
    Controller --> Client: 200 OK + предупреждения
end

deactivate ProcessingService
deactivate Controller

@enduml